    • Trivia
      Caddo Lake is one of the only natural lakes in Texas, with some others being Green Lake and Natural Dam Lake.

    Review
    Featured review
    8/10

    Stick with it. It's worth it!!

    Now this may not be a great movie but it's definitely a good one. And once all is revealed highly original. I did guess it before ( after a couple of clues ) I knew the whole story but that didn't ruin the good twists toward the end. Two stories run parallel to each other and both get better and better. As many have said the movie starts of slow and uninteresting. During the first half hour my wife kept asking me what the heck the movie is about but after a couple of plot reveals the story tightens and weaves to come together in the end. O'Brian as always does a good job and is helped by an earnest supporting cast. Pacing also picks up in the second half. As aforementioned stick with it and you should enjoy it as much as we did.
    • terrylarosa
    • Oct 10, 2024
